      "text": "鵺",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653319504,
      "updated": 1653319504
    },
    {
      "id": "628ba777aff09e0000473629",
      "text": "日本に生息する[キメラ]の一種。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653319543,
      "updated": 1653319558
    },
    {
      "id": "628ba7a1aff09e000047362b",
      "text": "猿の顔、狸の胴体、虎の手足、蛇の尾。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653319585,
      "updated": 1653319585
    },
    {
      "id": "628ba75aaff09e00003114af",
      "text": "『[平家物語]』で鵺退治の場面が描かれている。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653319514,
      "updated": 1653319821
    },
