    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d44",
      "text": "from [2023/08/01]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901873
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d45",
      "text": "のりしろ：[鵼の碑]発売トークより…",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901902
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d46",
      "text": " [- 鵺、変換で出ないらしいと聞いて入力したら一発で出て草][Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d47",
      "text": " \t[- さすが Google Keyboard]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d48",
      "text": " \tと思ったけど正しくは [\" 空+鳥] の方なのだろうか",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d49",
      "text": " \t\tそうっぽい",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d4a",
      "text": " \t\tむしろどのルートで探しても出てこなくて草",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d4b",
      "text": " \t\t　👀[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d4c",
      "text": " \t\t\t「ぬえ」「ぬえどり」「ぬえてき」",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d4d",
      "text": " \t\t\t[- てき、音符っぽいなー(深く調べてない)][cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d4e",
      "text": " \t\t\t　[- 液や腋、など「夜」の音？]何も関係なかったわ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d4f",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d50",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t> 精選版 日本国語大辞典 「鵼的」の意味・読み・例文・類語",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d51",
      "text": "      > ぬえ‐てき【鵼的】",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d52",
      "text": "      > 〘形動〙 どちらともつかないあいまいな様子。正体の知れないあやしげなさま。「鵼的人物」",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d53",
      "text": "      > ※穏健なる自由思想家（1910）〈魚住折蘆〉「思ふに今日生温(ぬる)き自由思想家の横行するは鵺(ヌエ)的革命たる明治維新の結果である」",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d54",
      "text": "      [https://kotobank.jp/word/鵼的-593967 鵼的(ぬえてき)とは？ 意味や使い方 - コトバンク]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d55",
      "text": " \t\t\t「こう」297個もあるので探すのを断念",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d56",
      "text": " \t\t\t「ぬえ」→単漢字→鵼で見つけた[wogikaze.icon]",
      "userId": "616ca537c25a92001e5f1e0d",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d57",
      "text": " \t\t鵺関連の表記気になる[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d58",
      "text": " \t\t　古事類苑見たら類聚名義抄、下学集などに載ってるっぽい",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d59",
      "text": " \t\t　　https://ys.nichibun.ac.jp/kojiruien/?cmd=search2&q=鵺",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d5a",
      "text": " \t\t　高名な鵺といえば[源頼政]の逸話関連だ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d5b",
      "text": " \t\t　　平家物語や源平盛衰記にあったはず",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d5c",
      "text": " \t\t　[以津真天]って鵺と関連してたっけ？",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d5d",
      "text": " \t\t　\t[あなたが分からないなら他の誰が分かるっていうんですか][Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91d705e90c00000590d5e",
      "text": " \t\t　\t私妖怪非専門、もっと詳しい人の一人や二人いるでしょ()[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901873,
      "updated": 1690901905
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91db05e90c000009c34ed",
      "text": " 鵺、雷と何らかの関係があった覚えがある[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901936,
      "updated": 1690901943
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91db05e90c000009c34ee",
      "text": " 　https://amenofuchikoma.net/2020/05/31/youkai-nue/?amp",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901936,
      "updated": 1690901943
    },
    {
      "id": "64c91db05e90c000009c34ef",
      "text": " 　[雷獣]なるものがいるらしいがどのへんに載ってんだろ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690901936,
      "updated": 1690901943
